==== Opener's third bid

*With three of responder's major and four of other major, opener bids:* +
@ [lavender-bg]#up-the-line with a minimum# +
@ [lavender-bg]#other major with a maximum#

*Otherwise opener's third bid, in order of priority, is:* +
@ two of unbid major = four-card suit,
_ ambiguous strength, F1 +
@ two of responder's major = three-card support,
_ minimum, NF +
@ three of responder's major = three-card support,
_ maximum +
@ 2NT = minimum +
@ 3NT = maximum

